		<title>Africa’s creator economy has a payment problem. These startups want to fix it.</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/06/02/francophone-weekly-by-techcabal-025/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Lina Kacyem]]></dc:creator>
